for this is the meal that heals.

00:22:56.880 --> 00:22:59.029
You're a good God, and You love us so

00:22:59.039 --> 00:23:02.390
much and You've provided so much for us in

00:23:02.390 --> 00:23:02.400
Jesus'name.

00:23:02.400 --> 00:23:06.630
Amen.

00:23:06.640 --> 00:23:08.070
See how it's different even than last

00:23:08.080 --> 00:23:11.669
time? I tried to

00:23:11.679 --> 00:23:13.830
tell Dina, we aren't religious up in

00:23:13.840 --> 00:23:15.830
here;

00:23:15.840 --> 00:23:17.990
we're just relationship.

00:23:18.000 --> 00:23:21.029
I just want Him to come and visit me.

00:23:21.039 --> 00:23:23.990
I look for Him every day,

00:23:24.000 --> 00:23:27.029
and I find Him. Even today,

00:23:27.039 --> 00:23:29.510
when we were out there in the

00:23:29.520 --> 00:23:31.270
garage

00:23:31.280 --> 00:23:33.510
cleaning and doing

00:23:33.520 --> 00:23:35.590
things, He started speaking about the

00:23:35.600 --> 00:23:38.230
end times to us,

00:23:38.240 --> 00:23:41.430
having impartation with His love

00:23:41.440 --> 00:23:43.510
and His fellowship,

00:23:45.760 --> 00:23:48.549
talking about end-time stuff, the

00:23:48.559 --> 00:23:50.630
healings, and the manifestations of the

00:23:50.640 --> 00:23:52.310
glory.

00:23:52.320 --> 00:23:57.110
I cherish those moments,

00:23:57.120 --> 00:23:57.990
don't you?

00:24:01.120 --> 00:24:04.710
Nothing else matters to me.

00:24:04.720 --> 00:24:06.870
I thought if

00:24:06.880 --> 00:24:09.190
you had to start over, you'd do the same

00:24:09.200 --> 00:24:11.110
thing: seek

00:24:11.120 --> 00:24:13.590
Him.

00:24:13.600 --> 00:24:15.110
Everything else He always provides. He

00:24:15.120 --> 00:24:17.750
always takes care of His people. If

00:24:17.760 --> 00:24:19.430
you're doing right and

00:24:19.440 --> 00:24:20.870
you're sowing into good ground and you're

00:24:20.880 --> 00:24:23.110
doing the word and apply the word and

00:24:23.120 --> 00:24:25.590
do what the word says to do,

00:24:25.600 --> 00:24:27.269
you'll lack no good thing.

00:24:27.279 --> 00:24:29.750
Everything else falls in place.

00:24:29.760 --> 00:24:31.669
It's when you get off in

00:24:31.679 --> 00:24:33.990
left field and you think you're on the

00:24:34.000 --> 00:24:36.070
right road and you keep doing the same

00:24:36.080 --> 00:24:39.350
thing expecting different results.

00:24:39.360 --> 00:24:42.630
I learned if you

00:24:42.640 --> 00:24:46.070
don't see results within six

00:24:46.080 --> 00:24:49.430
months to a quarter of a year, stop

00:24:49.440 --> 00:24:52.390
doing it.

00:24:52.400 --> 00:24:55.750
Apply pressure somewhere else; practice,

00:24:55.750 --> 00:24:55.760
and

00:24:55.760 --> 00:24:58.310
you'll start to see a change.

00:25:05.200 --> 00:25:09.110
A cruise ship takes a while

00:25:09.120 --> 00:25:11.190
to change course because it's such a

00:25:11.200 --> 00:25:13.830
big boat, but you instantaneously start

00:25:13.840 --> 00:25:16.310
to see it change. Even if you don't see

00:25:16.320 --> 00:25:18.310
the full manifestation of a turnaround,

00:25:18.320 --> 00:25:21.990
you still see change.

00:25:22.000 --> 00:25:23.990
You can feel it in the spirit.

00:25:24.000 --> 00:25:26.149
We're on the right road.

00:25:26.159 --> 00:25:28.390
You have an inward

00:25:28.400 --> 00:25:31.269
knowing. Be sensitive to what the Spirit

00:25:31.279 --> 00:25:33.510
of God is telling you to do.

00:25:33.520 --> 00:25:36.630
Even if you get off track, He

00:25:38.070 --> 00:25:38.080
said—I'm

00:25:40.880 --> 00:25:42.950
trying to find the right

00:25:45.909 --> 00:25:45.919
scripture—'You're

00:25:47.360 --> 00:25:48.789
not big enough to mess your

00:25:48.799 --> 00:25:49.830
life

00:25:49.830 --> 00:25:49.840
up.'He

00:25:49.840 --> 00:25:52.390
said, "No, you're not big enough

00:25:52.400 --> 00:25:54.950
to mess your life up,

00:25:54.950 --> 00:25:54.960
Braden,"because

00:25:54.960 --> 00:25:57.269
the footsteps of the righteous

00:25:57.279 --> 00:25:59.590
are ordered of the Lord.

00:26:10.400 --> 00:26:12.710
As

00:26:12.720 --> 00:26:14.390
long as you're upright and in right

00:26:14.400 --> 00:26:16.070
standing with Me, if you're

00:26:16.080 --> 00:26:19.269
seeking Me, the footsteps of the

00:26:19.279 --> 00:26:22.470
righteous are ordered of the Lord

00:26:22.480 --> 00:26:24.710
regardless. You can't mess your life

00:26:24.720 --> 00:26:27.350
up even if you tried.

00:26:27.360 --> 00:26:29.510
I mean, you

00:26:29.520 --> 00:26:31.029
can be stupid,

00:26:31.039 --> 00:26:33.430
but you can turn

00:26:33.440 --> 00:26:34.710
it around. That was

00:26:34.720 --> 00:26:36.230
all about Megan when I said, "Man,

00:26:36.240 --> 00:26:37.830
what are we ever going to

00:26:37.840 --> 00:26:40.149
do? How are we ever going to fix

00:26:40.149 --> 00:26:40.159
this?"I

00:26:40.159 --> 00:26:43.430
said, "Lord, I'm seeking You,

00:26:43.440 --> 00:26:45.350
and You're going to turn

00:26:45.360 --> 00:26:47.190
what the devil meant for bad

00:26:47.200 --> 00:26:49.990
around for

00:26:49.990 --> 00:26:50.000
good."I

00:26:50.000 --> 00:26:51.750
just believe that's where we are

00:26:51.750 --> 00:26:51.760
in

00:26:51.760 --> 00:26:55.190
these end times.

00:26:59.200 --> 00:27:00.470
Pray.

00:27:02.080 --> 00:27:03.590
Yep.

00:27:03.600 --> 00:27:07.110
I'm so full, baby.

00:27:07.120 --> 00:27:08.950
It's like

00:27:08.960 --> 00:27:11.430
poking a sponge; I'm going to

00:27:11.440 --> 00:27:13.430
dump. It's what happens every

00:27:13.440 --> 00:27:16.950
time. I go because I'm full.

00:27:16.960 --> 00:27:21.190
I stay full.

00:27:21.200 --> 00:27:24.549
Father, we just

00:27:24.559 --> 00:27:27.669
thank You.

00:27:31.679 --> 00:27:33.269
We

00:27:33.279 --> 00:27:35.350
praise You and we lift up this time

00:27:35.360 --> 00:27:42.230
of prayer.

00:27:42.240 --> 00:27:44.070
Whatever You want us to do, we'll

00:27:44.080 --> 00:27:46.230
do it. However You want us to pray,

00:27:46.240 --> 00:27:50.789
we'll pray.

00:28:24.559 --> 00:28:28.389
We open the eyes of our heart, Lord.

00:28:28.399 --> 00:28:32.310
We seek You and we find You. We'll knock

00:28:32.320 --> 00:28:34.950
and the door will be opened unto us.

00:28:34.960 --> 00:28:36.870
Father, there are so many things going on

00:28:36.880 --> 00:28:40.549
right now in the world,

00:28:40.559 --> 00:28:42.230
but I'm just going to follow Your

00:28:42.240 --> 00:28:45.830
Spirit. You lead, I follow.

00:28:45.840 --> 00:28:49.750
You lead, I follow.

00:28:49.760 --> 00:29:16.070
And Father, we just worship you.

00:29:16.080 --> 00:29:18.789
Oh Lord,

00:29:18.799 --> 00:29:24.870
you're beautiful.

00:29:24.880 --> 00:29:27.990
Your face

00:29:28.000 --> 00:29:30.470
is all

00:29:30.480 --> 00:29:35.430
I seek.

00:29:35.440 --> 00:29:37.909
And when

00:29:37.919 --> 00:29:40.470
your eyes

00:29:40.480 --> 00:29:42.549
are on

00:29:42.559 --> 00:29:46.149
this child,

00:29:46.159 --> 00:29:48.789
your grace

00:29:48.799 --> 00:29:50.710
abounds

00:29:50.720 --> 00:29:57.909
to me.

00:29:57.919 --> 00:30:00.710
Oh Lord,

00:30:00.720 --> 00:30:08.389
you're beautiful.

00:30:08.399 --> 00:30:11.510
Your face

00:30:11.520 --> 00:30:13.990
is all

00:30:14.000 --> 00:30:15.909
I

00:30:15.919 --> 00:30:18.070
seek.

00:30:18.080 --> 00:30:20.870
I'm seeing something.

00:30:20.880 --> 00:30:23.350
Isn't that amazing? All right, cool.

00:30:23.360 --> 00:30:25.110
It starts to shift the

00:30:25.120 --> 00:30:28.070
atmosphere.

00:30:28.080 --> 00:30:31.510
It's worship.

00:30:31.520 --> 00:30:34.710
It's worship

00:30:34.720 --> 00:30:38.470
in the presence

00:30:38.480 --> 00:30:43.269
of Jehovah

00:30:43.279 --> 00:30:46.950
God Almighty,

00:30:46.960 --> 00:30:51.990
Prince of Peace.

00:30:52.000 --> 00:30:53.590
Troubles

00:30:53.600 --> 00:30:58.789
vanish,

00:30:58.799 --> 00:31:04.470
hearts are mended

00:31:04.480 --> 00:31:10.310
in the presence

00:31:10.320 --> 00:31:16.710
of the king.

00:31:16.720 --> 00:31:20.516
In the presence

00:31:24.559 --> 00:31:26.230
of

00:31:26.240 --> 00:31:28.376
Jehovah,

00:31:31.039 --> 00:31:33.616
God Almighty,

00:31:37.039 --> 00:31:46.630
Prince of Peace.

