I see three

00:31:51.269 --> 00:31:51.279
I-Atlas.

00:31:51.279 --> 00:31:53.590
It's glowing.

00:31:53.600 --> 00:32:00.389
I don't know why I'm seeing this rock.

00:32:00.399 --> 00:32:02.070
It's traveling, but it's gotten

00:32:02.080 --> 00:32:05.430
brighter

00:32:05.440 --> 00:32:14.950
than the visions I've seen before.

00:32:14.960 --> 00:32:23.430
Why are so many focused on this?

00:32:23.440 --> 00:32:44.950
What is it about this?

00:32:44.960 --> 00:32:48.230
Something is coming.

00:32:48.240 --> 00:32:50.630
That's what I heard. 'Something is

00:32:50.640 --> 00:32:53.990
coming, son.

00:32:54.000 --> 00:33:01.669
Something is

00:33:01.679 --> 00:33:16.870
coming.'And

00:33:16.880 --> 00:33:20.389
this is not an alien.

00:33:20.399 --> 00:33:22.950
There's no such thing as aliens. It's

00:33:22.960 --> 00:33:25.750
demonic spirits.

00:33:25.760 --> 00:33:28.149
But what you're about to see is what

00:33:28.159 --> 00:33:31.110
Oral Roberts saw

00:33:31.120 --> 00:33:43.269
in 2004, called the wakeup call.

00:33:43.279 --> 00:33:46.310
For it will be a wake up to

00:33:46.320 --> 00:33:48.470
the church,

00:33:48.480 --> 00:33:51.990
a wake up to the world,

00:33:52.000 --> 00:33:54.389
a sign of the second coming of the Lord

00:33:54.399 --> 00:33:59.590
Jesus Christ.

00:33:59.600 --> 00:34:02.149
It's time for preachers

00:34:02.159 --> 00:34:05.190
to preach fire back in the pulpits,

00:34:05.200 --> 00:34:07.190
to preach repentance back in the

00:34:07.200 --> 00:34:09.909
pulpits.

00:34:09.919 --> 00:34:13.829
For there will be a sign in the heavens.

00:34:13.839 --> 00:34:15.750
There will be a sign throughout the

00:34:15.760 --> 00:34:21.270
earth

00:34:21.280 --> 00:34:24.310
daily.

00:34:24.320 --> 00:34:26.550
Remember this

00:34:29.679 --> 00:34:35.510
word

00:34:35.520 --> 00:34:50.118
over 20 years ago.

00:35:00.240 --> 00:35:06.494
He saw it. Timing was not right.

00:35:06.504 --> 00:35:07.910
You know, whenever you're

00:35:07.910 --> 00:35:07.920
seeing

00:35:07.920 --> 00:35:10.310
over in the spirit, it looks like it's

00:35:10.320 --> 00:35:17.990
right in front of your face.

00:35:18.000 --> 00:35:21.750
That's what the Lord

00:35:21.750 --> 00:35:21.760
said—that

00:35:21.760 --> 00:35:23.270
things look like they're right in

00:35:23.280 --> 00:35:25.829
front of your face,

00:35:25.839 --> 00:35:36.630
but you're looking in decades.

00:35:36.640 --> 00:35:43.750
But there's something coming.

00:35:43.760 --> 00:35:53.910
And most of the government knows that it's coming,

00:36:07.680 --> 00:36:12.069
and it's not

00:36:12.079 --> 00:36:13.829
conspiracy. No,

00:36:13.839 --> 00:36:18.069
it's not.

00:36:18.079 --> 00:36:19.109
But that's what the Spirit of the Lord

00:36:19.119 --> 00:36:20.550
just said. He said, 'This is not

00:36:20.560 --> 00:36:22.710
conspiracy.

00:36:22.720 --> 00:36:24.470
It's a sign of the second coming of the

00:36:24.480 --> 00:36:27.430
Lord Jesus Christ.'It's

00:36:27.430 --> 00:36:27.440
awakening

00:36:27.440 --> 00:36:31.510
the world.

00:36:40.079 --> 00:36:43.270
You have that clip of Oral Roberts? It was a

00:36:43.280 --> 00:36:45.670
short.

00:37:02.240 --> 00:37:09.270
It's on the Word Channel.

00:37:09.280 --> 00:37:10.630
You can play it. This is it.

00:37:10.640 --> 00:37:12.870
Yep, that's it.

00:37:14.320 --> 00:37:17.430
Just play it. I feel the Holy Ghost so

00:37:17.440 --> 00:37:19.270
strong.

00:37:19.280 --> 00:37:21.270
It's welling in my belly.

00:37:21.280 --> 00:37:24.310
Then I saw with my eyes something I'd

00:37:24.320 --> 00:37:26.870
never seen.

00:37:26.880 --> 00:37:28.630
Suddenly

00:37:28.640 --> 00:37:31.829
in the clouds in the skies

00:37:31.839 --> 00:37:35.510
above New York City and the east part of

00:37:35.520 --> 00:37:37.670
the United

00:37:37.670 --> 00:37:37.680
States—which

00:37:37.680 --> 00:37:41.990
hung there for quite some time

00:37:42.000 --> 00:37:45.349
and then spread out across America

00:37:45.359 --> 00:37:48.069
without touching the

00:37:48.069 --> 00:37:48.079
ground—and

00:37:48.079 --> 00:37:51.670
then God diffused it away from

00:37:51.680 --> 00:37:54.710
America and sent it out to the nations

00:37:54.720 --> 00:37:57.190
of the earth.

00:37:57.200 --> 00:37:59.589
And I saw

00:37:59.599 --> 00:38:01.670
and I heard.

00:38:04.320 --> 00:38:08.230
I saw something coming down from above.

00:38:08.240 --> 00:38:11.510
Smoke and vapor

00:38:11.520 --> 00:38:15.510
and blood. Or it looked like that to my

00:38:15.520 --> 00:38:19.030
spiritual eyes.

00:38:19.040 --> 00:38:24.230
There it was hanging so huge until it

00:38:24.240 --> 00:38:28.390
almost blotted out the sky.

00:38:28.400 --> 00:38:31.670
Instantly I thought about

00:38:31.680 --> 00:38:33.750
9/11

00:38:33.760 --> 00:38:35.670
when the terrorists attacked the Twin

00:38:35.680 --> 00:38:37.190
Towers.

00:38:37.200 --> 00:38:39.990
First I saw this thing

00:38:40.000 --> 00:38:41.670
hovering

00:38:41.680 --> 00:38:44.710
and great changes coming in it to where

00:38:44.720 --> 00:38:49.030
I couldn't miss it. And then I heard

00:38:49.040 --> 00:38:52.630
something.

00:38:52.640 --> 00:38:54.870
It reminded me of what a friend of

00:38:54.880 --> 00:38:59.829
mine had said when the first space

00:38:59.839 --> 00:39:01.829
capsule

00:39:01.839 --> 00:39:05.510
was released into the sky.

00:39:08.720 --> 00:39:12.230
He was a newsman in New York City. They told

00:39:12.230 --> 00:39:12.240
them to

00:39:12.240 --> 00:39:17.190
be a half mile or more away

00:39:17.200 --> 00:39:20.150
from the capsule.

00:39:20.160 --> 00:39:22.550
And he said when that thing lifted off

00:39:22.560 --> 00:39:26.630
the earth, there was a sound,

00:39:26.640 --> 00:39:31.349
and the sound itself moved the weeds and

00:39:31.359 --> 00:39:35.750
the growth. He said it penetrated

00:39:35.760 --> 00:39:39.190
my body. As I talked to others,

00:39:39.200 --> 00:39:41.589
they felt the same thing. He said the

00:39:41.599 --> 00:39:46.150
sound was so enormous that nothing had

00:39:46.160 --> 00:39:48.390
ever happened like it in the history of

00:39:48.400 --> 00:39:51.190
the world. Instantly I thought of that

00:39:51.200 --> 00:39:53.030
because the sound that was coming

00:39:53.040 --> 00:39:56.870
into my ears was penetrating my whole

00:39:56.880 --> 00:39:59.190
being.

00:39:59.200 --> 00:40:02.790
And then I heard God's voice.

00:40:02.800 --> 00:40:07.750
He said, 'I'm making a

00:40:07.750 --> 00:40:07.760
sign.'This

00:40:07.760 --> 00:40:09.990
is a sign according to the second

00:40:10.000 --> 00:40:13.349
chapter of Acts where the Apostle Peter,

00:40:13.359 --> 00:40:16.310
upon the giving of

00:40:16.320 --> 00:40:18.310
the Holy Spirit, the baptism of the Holy

00:40:18.320 --> 00:40:19.270
Spirit,

00:40:19.280 --> 00:40:21.190
said, 'There'll be signs

00:40:21.190 --> 00:40:21.200
in

00:40:21.750 --> 00:40:21.760
the

00:40:21.760 --> 00:40:22.870
skies.'He

00:40:22.880 --> 00:40:25.190
said, 'This is one of the

00:40:25.200 --> 00:40:29.910
signs of the end time because

00:40:29.920 --> 00:40:33.270
the world is not ready for the second

00:40:33.280 --> 00:40:35.990
coming of my son.'They are coming to

00:40:36.000 --> 00:40:39.190
church on Sunday morning mostly for

00:40:39.200 --> 00:40:40.950
themselves.

00:40:40.960 --> 00:40:44.390
And the preachers, for the most part, are

00:40:44.400 --> 00:40:46.790
not really concerned about the nations

00:40:46.800 --> 00:40:49.510
of the earth. They're concerned about

00:40:49.520 --> 00:40:52.790
the little group that is there, and they

00:40:52.800 --> 00:40:54.790
sing their songs and they get up

00:40:54.800 --> 00:40:59.910
and preach. When 9/11 struck,

00:40:59.920 --> 00:41:02.710
there was a fear that came

00:41:02.720 --> 00:41:06.069
into the hearts even of my people, of

00:41:06.079 --> 00:41:09.270
the church and of people outside the

00:41:09.280 --> 00:41:13.349
church, and millions the following Sunday

00:41:13.349 --> 00:41:13.359
rushed

00:41:13.359 --> 00:41:16.230
to go to church.

00:41:16.240 --> 00:41:18.710
But the preachers were not

00:41:18.720 --> 00:41:21.750
prepared, and most of them didn't even

00:41:21.760 --> 00:41:24.230
preach on it and didn't even talk about

00:41:24.240 --> 00:41:27.750
it being the sign of something that's

00:41:27.760 --> 00:41:30.390
coming

00:41:30.400 --> 00:41:34.390
hundreds of thousands of times bigger.

00:41:34.400 --> 00:41:37.829
He said when those planes of the

00:41:37.839 --> 00:41:41.109
terrorists struck the Twin Towers in New

00:41:41.119 --> 00:41:44.390
York City and they gradually came

00:41:44.400 --> 00:41:46.950
tumbling down,

00:41:46.960 --> 00:41:49.270
it was something bigger than people had

00:41:49.280 --> 00:41:51.750
ever seen, but it's

00:41:51.760 --> 00:41:55.270
nothing in comparison to what's going to

00:41:55.280 --> 00:41:59.990
happen in the second coming of my son.

00:42:00.000 --> 00:42:03.270
And so he said, 'My church was not

00:42:03.280 --> 00:42:06.069
prepared to deal with that.'And people

00:42:06.079 --> 00:42:08.630
came to church and then nothing much

00:42:08.640 --> 00:42:10.550
happened, and they dropped back, and many

00:42:10.560 --> 00:42:12.550
of them went back to their bars.

00:42:12.560 --> 00:42:15.030
There's a sign coming.

00:42:15.040 --> 00:42:18.069
We're going to pray into that now.

